      "span_text": "Indeed, lower CSF MTf were associated with greater cognitive deficits (ADAS-Cog13) in MCI and lower hippocampal volumes in both CN and MCI. While not associated with hippocampal volume, CSF MTf was associated with longitudinal hippocampal volume change in AD. MTf appears to have a role in mediating cellular iron uptake  , and hence likely to be involved in iron metabolism."
